    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When I retrieve the validators from a file element nothing is returned
But! if i call the getTransferAdapter for the element, and call on it the getValidators I do get the validators</p>

<p>example</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$file = new Zend_Form_Element_File('image');
$file-&gt;addValidator('Count', false, 1);
print_r($file-&gt;getValidators()); // nothing is retrieved
        
$adapter = $file-&gt;getTransferAdapter();
print_r($adapter-&gt;getValidators()); // i get my validators
</code></pre>

